Date of Birth: March 21, 1872<br/>
Birthplace: Salt Lake City, Utah, USA<br/>
Ordained apostle: October 24, 1901<br/>
Death: January 23, 1918<br/>
<br/>
Born March 21, 1872, at Salt Lake City, Salt Lake Co., Utah, to Joseph Fielding Smith and Edna Lambson. Ordained apostle Oct. 24, 1901, by Joseph F. Smith, at age 29; died Jan. 23, 1918, at Salt Lake City, Salt Lake Co., Utah, at age 45.